CurrentAffairs—NewsAggregatorWebApp

Afull-stacknewsaggregatorwebapplicationthatfetchesanddisplaysreal-timenewsacrossmultiplecategoriesusingtheNewsAPI.BuiltwithHTML,CSSandJavaScript.

---

Features

-BreakingNewsTicker—Livescrollingheadlinesatthetop
-7NewsCategories—India,TopNews,Technology,Sports,Entertainment,Business,Science&Health
-AutoSlider—Top5heronewscardsslideautomaticallywithdotindicatorsandarrows
-Search—Searchanytopicfromthesidebarwithtrendingquick-tags
-DarkMode—TogglewithpreferencesavedinlocalStorage
-LoadMore—Paginationtoloadmorearticlespercategory
-Authentication—LoginandSignupwithformvalidationandsessionmanagement

---

TechStack

|Layer    |Technology|
|Frontend |HTML5,CSS3,JavaScript(ES6+)|
|NewsAPI  |[NewsAPI.org](https://newsapi.org)|
|Hosting  |LiveServer/Render|
